{
  "texts": [
    "ShareGPT90K foot_27 and Open-Chat (Wang et al, 2023a) have compiled tens of thousands of real conversations from ShareGPT.",
    "ShareGPT-Chinese-English-90k 32 provides human-machine Q&A data in parallel Chinese-English corpora.",
    "ShareChat 33 translates all acquired ShareGPT data into Chinese.",
    "LMSYS-Chat-1M (Zheng et al, 2023a) has gathered real conversation data from 25 LLMs between April and August 2023.",
    "When constructing datasets, a combination of the first two methods can be employed."
  ]
}